								<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">As the leader in digital skills training and one of the largest professional communities, BrainStation’s blog is the ultimate hub for career advice, industry insights, and thought leadership in the career and tech landscape.&nbsp;</span></p>



<p>If you’re looking for something to help you boost your digital skills, take a look at our most popular career development posts.</p>



<h3><a href="https://brainstation.io/blog/why-learning-styles-are-a-myth-and-how-we-really-learn"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Why Learning Styles are a Myth (and How We Really Learn)</span></a></h3>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"><a href="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Zachary_Monteiro_Different_Learning_stypes-e1569420936110.png"><img src="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Zachary_Monteiro_Different_Learning_stypes-1024x353.png" alt="Are learning styles a myth?" class="wp-image-7598"/></a></figure></div>



<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Last year, thirty eminent professors and doctors of psychology and neuroscience published an open letter in The Guardian declaring the concept of learning styles a “neuromyth.” So, what’s wrong with these learning styles?&nbsp;</span></p>



<h3><a href="https://brainstation.io/blog/why-reskilling-is-the-new-hiring"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Why Reskilling is the New Hiring</span></a></h3>



<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">It’s now cheaper to reskill current employees than to hire new ones. Take a closer look at the differences between reskilling and upskilling, and how you can use them to future-proof your business.</span></p>



<h3><a href="https://brainstation.io/blog/how-5-ceos-used-design-thinking-to-transform-their-companies"><span style="font-weight: 400;">How 5 CEOs used Design Thinking to Transform their Companies</span></a></h3>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"><a href="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Untitled3.png"><img src="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Untitled3-1024x578.png" alt="How CEOs use design thinking" class="wp-image-7593" srcset="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Untitled3-1024x578.png 1024w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Untitled3-300x169.png 300w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Untitled3-768x433.png 768w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Untitled3-960x542.png 960w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></figure></div>



<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Read about top CEOs leveraging a human-centered approach to create innovative, successful companies.</span></p>



<h3><a href="https://brainstation.io/blog/seven-startups-leading-the-nyc-tech-boom"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Seven Startups Leading the NYC Tech Boom</span></a></h3>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"><a href="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/GettyImages-908031820-e1562186397855.jpg"><img src="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/GettyImages-908031820-e1562186397855-1024x535.jpg" alt="New York City Tech Scene" class="wp-image-9242" srcset="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/GettyImages-908031820-e1562186397855-1024x535.jpg 1024w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/GettyImages-908031820-e1562186397855-300x157.jpg 300w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/GettyImages-908031820-e1562186397855-768x401.jpg 768w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/GettyImages-908031820-e1562186397855-960x501.jpg 960w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/GettyImages-908031820-e1562186397855.jpg 2121w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></figure></div>



<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">New York City’s tech scene continues to boom…and homegrown startups are playing a huge role. Take a look at seven startups that are paving the way for the Big Apple’s emerging tech sector.&nbsp;</span></p>



<h3><a href="https://brainstation.io/blog/5-reasons-why-torontos-tech-industry-continues-to-soar"><span style="font-weight: 400;">5 Reasons Why Toronto&#8217;s Tech Industry Continues to Soar</span></a></h3>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"><a href="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Zachary_Monteiro_Behind_TOs_Tech_Surge.png"><img src="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Zachary_Monteiro_Behind_TOs_Tech_Surge-1024x353.png" alt="Toronto tech industry" class="wp-image-7790" srcset="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Zachary_Monteiro_Behind_TOs_Tech_Surge-1024x353.png 1024w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Zachary_Monteiro_Behind_TOs_Tech_Surge-300x103.png 300w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Zachary_Monteiro_Behind_TOs_Tech_Surge-768x265.png 768w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Zachary_Monteiro_Behind_TOs_Tech_Surge-960x331.png 960w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Zachary_Monteiro_Behind_TOs_Tech_Surge-331x115.png 331w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Zachary_Monteiro_Behind_TOs_Tech_Surge-1160x400.png 1160w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Zachary_Monteiro_Behind_TOs_Tech_Surge-2320x800.png 2320w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></figure></div>



<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Toronto didn’t become a worldwide tech hub overnight. In fact, it was a years-long process. So, what are the factors underpinning that supersonic growth? Take a closer look at how Toronto got where it is today and why it will continue to grow.</span></p>



<h3><a href="https://brainstation.io/blog/vancouvers-tech-market-is-booming-but-its-missing-one-thing-talent"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Vancouver&#8217;s Tech Market is Booming, but it&#8217;s Missing One Thing: Web Developers</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">&nbsp;</span></h3>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"><a href="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/spencer-watson-335298-unsplash-e1553108654908.jpg"><img src="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/spencer-watson-335298-unsplash-e1553108654908-1024x354.jpg" alt="Data jobs in Vancouver" class="wp-image-8512" srcset="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/spencer-watson-335298-unsplash-e1553108654908-1024x354.jpg 1024w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/spencer-watson-335298-unsplash-e1553108654908-300x104.jpg 300w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/spencer-watson-335298-unsplash-e1553108654908-768x266.jpg 768w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/spencer-watson-335298-unsplash-e1553108654908-960x332.jpg 960w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/spencer-watson-335298-unsplash-e1553108654908-331x115.jpg 331w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/spencer-watson-335298-unsplash-e1553108654908-662x230.jpg 662w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/spencer-watson-335298-unsplash-e1553108654908-1160x400.jpg 1160w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/spencer-watson-335298-unsplash-e1553108654908-2320x800.jpg 2320w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/spencer-watson-335298-unsplash-e1553108654908.jpg 2475w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></figure></div>



<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">When it comes to global tech hotspots, few can match the growth of Vancouver. But, with this tech boom, an unavoidable growing pain emerged: An abundance of tech opportunities and a shortage of skilled workers to fill those jobs. How can you take advantage of this skills gap?</span></p>



<h3><a href="https://brainstation.io/blog/how-apple-hires-the-best-its-all-about-skills"><span style="font-weight: 400;">How Apple Hires the Best: It’s All About Skills</span></a></h3>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"><a href="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/carles-rabada-GulyvMt9UwI-unsplash-e1575921577719.jpg"><img src="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/carles-rabada-GulyvMt9UwI-unsplash-e1575921559300-1024x502.jpg" alt="Apple does not require degree" class="wp-image-10202"/></a></figure></div>



<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Many big-name employers are now looking past rigid educational requirements to find the best talent, and this kind of thinking is catching on. Read why some of the world’s most innovative companies are changing their hiring practices.&nbsp;</span></p>



<h3><a href="https://brainstation.io/blog/digital-marketing-certifications-worth-time"><span style="font-weight: 400;">6 Digital Marketing Certificates Worth Your Time</span></a></h3>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"><a href="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Zachary_Monteiro_5_Certificates.png"><img src="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Zachary_Monteiro_5_Certificates-1024x353.png" alt="digital marketing certifications" class="wp-image-7413" srcset="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Zachary_Monteiro_5_Certificates-1024x353.png 1024w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Zachary_Monteiro_5_Certificates-300x103.png 300w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Zachary_Monteiro_5_Certificates-768x265.png 768w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Zachary_Monteiro_5_Certificates-960x331.png 960w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Zachary_Monteiro_5_Certificates-331x115.png 331w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Zachary_Monteiro_5_Certificates-1160x400.png 1160w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Zachary_Monteiro_5_Certificates-2320x800.png 2320w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></figure></div>



<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">When it comes to digital marketing, there’s always something you can learn (and in fact, there’s almost always something you should be learning). If you’re looking for additional training, here are six digital marketing certificates that are worth your time.</span></p>



<h3><a href="https://brainstation.io/blog/how-to-get-your-employer-to-pay-for-digital-skills-training"><span style="font-weight: 400;">How to get your Employer to Pay for Digital Skills Training&nbsp;</span></a></h3>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter"><a href="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Zachary_Monteiro_Pay_for_my_Training.png"><img src="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Zachary_Monteiro_Pay_for_my_Training-1024x353.png" alt="How to get your employer to pay for your training" class="wp-image-7448" srcset="https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Zachary_Monteiro_Pay_for_my_Training-1024x353.png 1024w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Zachary_Monteiro_Pay_for_my_Training-300x103.png 300w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Zachary_Monteiro_Pay_for_my_Training-768x265.png 768w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Zachary_Monteiro_Pay_for_my_Training-960x331.png 960w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Zachary_Monteiro_Pay_for_my_Training-331x115.png 331w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Zachary_Monteiro_Pay_for_my_Training-1160x400.png 1160w, https://d1jxdyr49kipv5.cloudfront.net/prod/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Zachary_Monteiro_Pay_for_my_Training-2320x800.png 2320w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></figure></div>



<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">By now, most professionals know that re-training and up-skilling is necessary to stay ahead in today’s job market. If your boss still needs convincing, here are some points that might help persuade them to invest in you and your future.&nbsp;</span></p>



<h3><a href="https://brainstation.io/blog/5-free-tools-to-make-data-science-easier"><span style="font-weight: 400;">5 Free Tools to Make Data Science Easier</span></a></h3>



