<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">One of the great things about data science is that many of the state-of-the-art tools used by Data Scientists are free. Here is a list of the best free software tools for working with data.</span></p>



<h3><a href="https://brainstation.io/blog/how-data-played-a-role-in-the-toronto-raptors-nba-championship"><span style="font-weight: 400;">How Data Played a Role in the NBA Championship</span></a></h3>



